I need a complete, production-ready tokenization platform built from the ground up. This isn’t a single smart contract or a quick proof-of-concept—I’m after an end-to-end solution that lets non-technical users create, issue, and manage their own tokens, trade them within an integrated marketplace, and optionally weave in reward or loyalty utilities.

Here’s the high-level picture of what I expect:

• Smart-contract layer: audited, upgradeable contracts for token creation, minting/burning, transfers, and marketplace listings. I’m open to Ethereum, BNB Smart Chain, Polygon, or whichever EVM network you recommend for cost and speed.
• Web application: modern, responsive UI/UX where users can log in (Web3 wallet plus optional email social-login), spin up a new token in a few clicks, view analytics, and manage liquidity or rewards.
• Trading module: internal order book or automated AMM hooks so users can swap, list, and purchase tokens without leaving the platform.
• Admin dashboard: role-based controls, fee settings, blacklisting, and full audit trails.
• Integrations: MetaMask, WalletConnect, and hardware-wallet compatibility; optional fiat on-ramp/off-ramp APIs if you’ve done those before.
• Compliance and security: KYC/AML plugin points, multi-sig admin keys, thorough test coverage, and at least one external audit report.

